# Atlarium MCP

Atlarium MCP is a public read-only Model Context Protocol server for structured
freshwater aquarium data.

Production MCP endpoint:

- https://mcp.atlarium.bio/mcp

Website:

- https://atlarium.bio

Available data:

- Freshwater aquarium fish
- Aquatic plants
- Aquarium products
- Water parameters
- Compatibility and stocking guidance
- Aquarium guides

Important limits:

- No write tools
- No user or workspace data
- No admin data
- Compatibility and suggestions are advisory and should be verified for each
  real aquarium setup
